OL,6,FFans gathered to pay tribute to Denis
OL,7,FLaw at Old Trafford.
OL,9,FManchester United have paid tribute to
OL,10,FDenis Law ahead of their 3-1 defeat to
OL,11,FBrighton this afternoon.
OL,13,FThe teams were led on to the Old
OL,14,FTrafford pitch by a bagpiper playing
OL,15,FFlower of Scotland before Sir Alex
OL,16,FFerguson, accompanied by Brian Kidd,
OL,17,FPaddy Crerand and Alex Stepney, laid a
OL,18,Fwreath, followed by a poetic tribute
OL,19,Fand a minute's applause.
