OL,3,CDenis Law was 'cornerstone' of
OL,4,CManchester United success
OL,6,F"He was the best Scottish player of
OL,7,Fall time," said Ferguson, who oversaw
OL,8,F13 Premier League titles and two
OL,9,FChampions League triumphs during his
OL,10,Fremarkable trophy-laden spell as
OL,11,FUnited manager.
OL,13,F"He was a fantastic player and an
OL,14,Fincredible human being. The great
OL,15,Fthing is that he did not use his fame,
OL,16,Fhe was so level-headed and down to
OL,17,Fearth and we are talking about a guy
OL,18,Fwho had all of these caps for Scotland
OL,19,Fand is called the 'King of Old
OL,20,FTrafford'.
OL,1,W~s1{$~k4{$k7                    G3/7
