OL,3,CDenis Law was 'cornerstone' of
OL,4,CManchester United success
OL,6,F"It is an interesting thing because
OL,7,Fwhy did they call him the King? You
OL,8,Fhad guys like George Best, Bobby
OL,9,FCharlton - the greatest English player
OL,10,Fof all time and a fantastic player for
OL,11,Four club - and they called Denis 'the
OL,12,FKing'.
OL,14,F"It was something to do with the
OL,15,Fdetermination and the will to win
OL,16,Fevery time he went on that football
OL,17,Ffield. He was a really competitive
OL,18,Fhuman being and it was a natural thing
OL,19,Ffor the supporters to associate with
OL,20,Fhim as their King."
