OL,3,CDenis Law was 'cornerstone' of
OL,4,CManchester United success
OL,6,FLaw made the move to Old Trafford from
OL,7,FTorino in 1962 before going on to
OL,8,Fscore 237 times, the club's third-
OL,9,Fhighest scorer in history behind Wayne
OL,10,FRooney and Charlton.
OL,12,FA year after he claimed the 1964
OL,13,FBallon d'Or, Law helped fire United to
OL,14,Ftheir first Division One title since
OL,15,Fthe Munich Air Disaster.
