OL,3,CDenis Law was 'cornerstone' of
OL,4,CManchester United success
OL,6,FHaving already won the FA Cup in 1963,
OL,7,FLaw inspired United to another league
OL,8,Ftitle in 1966-67 before Busby's side's
OL,9,Fgreatest achievement - European Cup
OL,10,Fglory - against Benfica. Law was
OL,11,Fdiagnosed with Alzheimer's disease and
OL,12,Fvascular dementia in 2021.
OL,14,FFerguson, 83, speaking to the United
OL,15,Fclub website, continued: "I went to
OL,16,Fsee him a couple of months ago and he
OL,17,Fwas not doing well.
OL,19,F"When he joined us, he turned the club
OL,20,Faround and that is the greatest thing
OL,21,Fhe could have done.
OL,1,W~s1{$~k4{$k7                    G6/7
