OL,3,CDenis Law was 'cornerstone' of
OL,4,CManchester United success
OL,6,F"Sir Matt was recovering from the
OL,7,FMunich Air Disaster and they won their
OL,8,Ffirst trophy in 1963, shortly after
OL,9,Fthey signed Denis. He was so vital to
OL,10,Fthe renovation of the team. He was a
OL,11,Fcornerstone of the club's future
OL,12,Fsuccess."
